headline: AI Workforce Consortium Finds 78% of ICT Roles Now Include AI Technical Skills, While Human Skills Gain Priority for Responsible Tech Adoption
summary: Today, the AI Workforce Consortium released its second study, "ICT in Motion: The Next Wave of AI Integration," which finds that AI roles now dominate tech market growth. Led by Cisco (NASDAQ: CSCO), the Consortium is a private sector collaboration that includes industry leaders Accenture, Cornerstone, Eightfold AI, Google, IBM, Indeed, Intel, Microsoft and SAP.
